DESCRIPTION:Are you wondering how to stand out and land your first role i
 n tech?&#13\;\n&#13\;\nBreaking into tech can feel overwhelming\, especi
 ally with so many candidates competing for the same opportunities. Knowi
 ng how to position yourself through your resume\, portfolio\, and interv
 iew skills can make all the difference.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nIn this live Tech
  Talk\, Mahindra Guman\, learning and development professional with exte
 nsive experience in recruitment and career coaching\, will share how new
  developers can effectively position themselves for success. He will cov
 er building a strong resume and portfolio\, preparing for interviews\, a
 nd practical job search strategies to help you stay motivated and consis
 tent.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nGet the actionable steps you need to stand out as a
  candidate\, whether you’re writing your first line of code or landing y
 our next interview.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nJoin us on Friday\, April 3 at 1 PM P
 T | 3 PM CT | 4 PM ET.&#13\;\nSave your spot now and take the next step 
 toward your first tech role.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nRSVP Here: https://www.meetu
 p.com/techacademy/events/\n\nTags: tech talk\, Career Coaching\, Career 
 Networking\, job search\, Job Interview\, technology\, Tech Industry\, s
 oftware engineering\, Computer Engineering\, coding\, programmers\, prog
 ramming\n\nImported from: http://calagator.org/events/1250482525
URL:https://meet.google.com/kdk-gbga-gnv
SUMMARY:Tech Talk | Breaking Into Tech: How New Developers Can Stand Out 
 with Mahindra Guman
LOCATION:The Tech Academy: 310 SW 4th Ave Suite 412\, Portland OR 97204 U
 SA
SEQUENCE:1
END:VEVENT
