 those newsletters in your email inbox? Got an RSS reader yet? Want your 
 very own RSS feed for your blog? We'll help you get set up!&#13\;\n&#13\
 ;\nRSS LIBERATES YOU.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nBut what do #pdx and RSS have in co
 mmon? A LOT! Try this. Download an RSS app on your phone. Go to @portlan
 dmercury@pdx.social's website. &quot\;Share&quot\; the link to your RSS 
 app\, and click Add Feed. Never miss a local story or event!\n\nTags: we
 b\n\nImported from: http://calagator.org/events/1250482520
URL:https://reeds.website/2026/webday
SUMMARY:Web Day: RSS Edition
LOCATION:Albina Library: false
SEQUENCE:1
END:VEVENT
