UID:http://calagator.org/events/1250482298
DESCRIPTION:Details&#13\;\n## What to Expect:&#13\;\nCode and Coffee is a
 n inclusive\, informal co-working session. Drink some coffee\, bring you
 r laptop\, and have engaging conversations. This is a great opportunity 
 to learn from others\, share your knowledge\, and possibly collaborate o
 n side projects\, online courses\, or even your day-to-day work tasks.&#
 13\;\nStill uncertain? Let's chat on Discord!&#13\;\n## Venue:&#13\;\nTh
 e Venue is at Roseline Café\, who is graciously allowing us to host a sp
 ace. WIFI\, power outlets&#13\;\nRecommended Parking: Smart Park\, $7 al
 l day https://www.portland.gov/transportation/parking/smartpark&#13\;\n&
 #13\;\n## Coffee:&#13\;\nRoseline Café has drip coffee and fixings avail
 able for it&#13\;\n&#13\;\n## Agenda:&#13\;\n10 AM - Arrival&#13\;\n10:1
 5 AM - Introductions:&#13\;\nShare your name&#13\;\nDiscuss your current
  projects or interests. If you don’t have a specific project\, share wha
 t intrigues you!&#13\;\nMention your expertise and how you can assist ot
 hers.&#13\;\nAre you job hunting or hiring? Let us know!&#13\;\nCommunit
 y events you wanna plug. If none\, that's cool too.&#13\;\n12:30 AM - Wr
 apping Up: You can stay longer\, but we'll officially be done! We usuall
 y grab lunch as a group at near by food carts\n\nImported from: http://c
 alagator.org/events/1250482298
URL:https://www.meetup.com/portland-code-coffee/
SUMMARY:Code & Coffee @ Roseline Café
LOCATION:Roseline Cafe: false
SEQUENCE:2
END:VEVENT
